divs: Sighting DetailsI was climbing up Mt Harvard in 2006 once I passed the tree line i turned around and took this photo of Mt. Yale. and did not notice anything out of the ordinary, it wasnt until i got home and downloaded my pictures and looked at them in there full size that I did noticed this object in the photo. I thought the object was an aircaft at first but I magnified the picture and cut (Picure 2) and then noticed it was no identifiable aircraft.
